      "writtenOn": "2018-11-05T18:31:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The root of the problem is that we want to use the value of a generator expression:\n\n$\u003cTARGET_FILE_DIR:${RUN_TARGET}\u003e which tells us which directory the generated target will end up in. This directory can change depending on the generator used. Xcode for example see to do something along the lines ${CMAKE_RUNTIME_OUTPUT_DIRECTORY}/${CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE}/${RUN_TARGET}. Whereas GNUMake/Ninja will use a single binplace directory (just like our old build system).",
